m. 1:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107467\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107467)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107467)\">Ezek. 22:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106684\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106684)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106684)\">Ps. 32:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107625\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107625)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107625)\">Joel 2:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107648\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107648)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107648)\">Obad. 1:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108450\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108450)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108450)\">Luke 4:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110286\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110286)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110286)\">Heb. 11:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111967\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111967)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111967)\">Alma 14:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}